Primitive data type
example : short, long, char, float etc...

Wrapper class
//Method to change variable (Use capital letter)
Example : Short, Long, Character, Float, Double, Byte, Integer etc...
Sample
Short myNewAge = 23;
double result = myNewAge.doubleValue();
System.out.println(result);
// In this case you will get 23.0 instead of 23

**enum (store a stable variable)
//promotion (convert small data type to big data type)
Example :
int avg = 2;
double newAvg = avg;
//casting (convert big data type to small data type)
Example :
double price = 12.3;
int singlePrice = (int) price;
//auto-boxing
int primitive = 100;
Integer newWrapper = primitive;
//unboxing
Double doubleOfWrapper = 34.4;
double primitiveDouble = doubleOfWrapper;

